Use 10 ms frames\&. 
.IP "\fBOPUS_FRAMESIZE_20_MS\fP" 1c
Use 20 ms frames\&. 
.IP "\fBOPUS_FRAMESIZE_40_MS\fP" 1c
Use 40 ms frames\&. 
.IP "\fBOPUS_FRAMESIZE_60_MS\fP" 1c
Use 60 ms frames\&. 
.IP "\fBOPUS_FRAMESIZE_80_MS\fP" 1c
