.RS 4
\fBOPUS_GET_FORCE_CHANNELS\fP 
.RE
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIx\fP \fCopus_int32\fP: Allowed values: 
.IP "\fB\fBOPUS_AUTO\fP\fP" 1c
Not forced (default) 
.IP "\fB1 \fP" 1c
Forced mono 
.IP "\fB2 \fP" 1c
Forced stereo 
.PP
.RE
